      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is literally impossible to reach and i hate being stuck with a high reading or a low reading. if i truly barely ate, wouldn't it be safer to just play it conservative and skip it? i'm just worried about a hypoglycemic episode since there was no carb intake.",
