      "content": "wait, \"take a dose\" of insulin to prevent a low? won't that make my blood sugar go even lower? i'm super confused, i thought if i don't eat, i shouldn't take insulin at all. if i take more insulin now without food, im gonna crash hard. are you sure that's what people actually do?",
